<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Glendale</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
        <p class="par-lg">With breathtaking views of the Rockies to the west, Glendale is a serene residential neighborhood located in the Southwest quadrant of Calgary. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">The major highlight of the Glendale real estate is the Optimist Athletic Park that supports a plethora of sports activities including soccer, softball, field hockey, lacrosse, and football. </p>
        <p class="par-lg">Shaped like a hammer, this iconic park houses 3 sports fields, 1 little league diamond and a total of 8 ball diamonds.</p>
        </div>
